# Introduction to the Fundamentals of CSS

**CSS (Cascading Style Sheets)**

CSS serves as the styling language for web development, enabling the design and presentation of HTML elements. Proficiency in CSS is crucial for crafting visually appealing and user-friendly websites. This introduction will delve into the fundamental principles and techniques of CSS, empowering you to enhance the aesthetics and layout of your web pages.

Throughout the subsequent sections, you'll discover in-depth explanations, practice exercises providing a comprehensive guide to understanding and applying CSS.